{
  "texts": [
    "Linear regression, logistic regression, and polynomial regression are popular regression algorithms (IBM, 2022a).",
    "Unsupervised learning analyzes and clusters unlabeled datasets.",
    "These algorithms discover hidden patterns or data groupings without the need for human intervention -without the need for labeling the datasets.",
    "In unsupervised learning, a machine is simply given a heap of data and told to make sense of it -to find patterns, regularities, and useful ways of condensing, representing, or visualizing it.",
    "(Christian, 2020a; IBM, 2022b)."
  ]
}